Usage:

    kanban

Actions on tasks

    kanban <task id> add
    kanban <task id> today      Move task to today's TODO list
    kanban <task id> start      Move task to WIP. Mark it as active 
    kanban <task id> done       Move task to done. Mark it as completed
    kanban <task id> block      Tag the task as BLOCKED
    kanban <task id> unblock    Remove the tag BLOCKED from the task


    
 

Reporting

    kanban

Sprint actions

    kanban

And finally

    kanban help         This help message
